-- Chevron says Pembroke refinery fully operational
-- 
-- Fri Jun 3, 2011 6:20am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/06/03/us-chevron-pembroke-idUSTRE75227V20110603

 

 LONDON  (Reuters) - Oil major Chevron ( CVX.N ) said on Friday that shift workers were at its UK Pembroke refinery and it remained fully operational following a fatal explosion at the site. 

 "The refinery remains fully operational and the shift staff are working," a spokeswoman for Chevron said. (Reporting by  Ikuko Kurahone ; editing by  Jason Neely )